text:
in class org.apache.catalina.connector.Connector
field's 

/** URI encoding as body. */
protected boolean useBodyEncodingForURI = false;

default value is false;

this causes that httpServletRequest.setCharacterEncoding("some-encoding")
doesn't affect requestURI decoding.

Think this should be changed  to 

protected boolean useBodyEncodingForURI = true;
